name: Sonic the Hedgehog
description: A fangame based on the Sonic the Hedgehog TV series, also known as Sonic SatAM.

name: Waifu Builder
description: Welcome to Waifu Builder- a relaxing puzzle game inspired by Model building(gunpla) but with just 100% waifus. You will experience the relaxing process of building a model kit with complete freedom with over 61 waifus.

name: I'd Kill You as a Worm
description: You turned into a worm and your boyfriend broke up with you. it's time to get revenge

name: DooM: Fall of Mars
description: A Doom RPG Fangame based on diablo series about a marine invading the evil bases on Phobos.

name: Kitsune's Paths
description: Protect the portals and aid the good spirits in this 2D tower defense game. Stop demons from invading by activating turrets along the paths. As the forest protector, use your speed and strategy to keep peace across the realms, transforming into the legendary nine-tailed fox to fulfill your destiny.

name: Trainz Railroad Simulator 2019: Pro Train - NS Heritage Loco Bundle 2
Trainz Railroad Simulator 2022: Pro Train - NS Heritage Loco Bundle 2
Trainz Plus Pro Train - NS Heritage Loco Bundle 2
Trainz Railroad Simulator 2022: Model Trainz - Chicago
Aeromachina
description: You are Bogey, an android evolved from the remains of abandoned aircraft – but fight and flight are the only things keeping you from returning to scrap. Battle across the remnants of Earth and solve humanity's disappearance in this nostalgic 3D Platformer Metroidvania!

name: Ballest of Them All
description: A physics-based platformer about smooth movement. Master your ball to earn medals on highly-replayable tracks, or climb the Tower to prove you're the Ballest of Them All.

name: Quickcast
description: A turn-based strategy roguelike game where you and your opponent share a single deck. Use matching rules to cast spells and collect powerful artifacts. Defeat wizards specializing in each element and absorb their powers to become the best wizard you can be.

name: A la Card
description: Buckle up for a roguelike deckbuilder boiling over with card mutation mischief and limitless synergies. It's a food-truck-themed deckbuilding roguelike all about bending the rules and letting the player get weird with absurd synergies.

name: Wild Growth
description: A short, action-packed incremental healer game set in a grim norse world.

name: Abyss Unchained
description: Upcoming indie 3D Metroidvania/Platformer game where you wield a heavy weight to traverse a labyrinthine mansion.

name: Chaos Machina
description: A fast-paced action RPG dungeon crawler with roguelike elements. Shoot, run, dodge, and upgrade your abilities to defeat enemies before Chaos consumes the level.

name: Trolling Bowling
description: A wild & fun multiplayer party game bowling simulator to compete with your friends, where it’s troll or be trolled. Sabotage your friends with trolling powers like concrete pins, oil spills, windmills, and more! Upgrade your bowling ball. Bowl to score points, collect rings, and send pins flying!

name: AutoGuessr
description: A browser Game based on geoguessr, where you have to guess the price of cars from given info

name: Ridiculous Shipping
description: Ridiculous Shipping is a strategy simulation game about running a chaotic sea port. Take charge of unique ports around the world, unload ships, and get every container to its destination using cranes, drones, trucks, and ridiculous buildings like shark-filled aquariums.

name: Seeker of the Ruins
description: As a fearless dwarf delver, navigate interesting underground labyrinths & ruins, uncover hidden treasures, solve riddles and hide from monsters. Use various items and potions to survive and outsmart environmental hazards in this immersive non-combat adventure. Delve into the unknown and reclaim lost treasures!

name: Piss Off
description: Control creatures with gross abilities and compete in absurd frantic battles in this action platformer game. Piss, spit, shit and make your friends taste every fluid you can get on them before they do the same to you. Try not to lose your hair and skin to the corrosive fluids of the other creatures and watch out for the aliens!

name: There's Nothing Underground
description: There's Nothing Underground is a roguelike puzzle adventure where you use random tools to solve levels in endless ways. Unlock and combine tools to tackle 100+ levels, each with unique challenges. Find creative solutions, uncover the asteroid's secrets, and survive!

name: Cursed Blood
description: Play as vengeful Samurai Apes fueled by blood in a lightning-fast mix of stealth and action. Spill blood, cut limbs and claim vengeance.

name: The Daruma Challenge
description: A brutal bouncing challenge. No shortcuts, no mercy—just you vs. gravity. How far will you climb before it all comes crashing down?

name: Edge of Sanity: Eldritch Edition
description: Explore a world of madness as you struggle to keep your humanity

name: The Northern Path
description: Embark on an adventure through the vast northern wilderness, where survival depends on your skills and instincts. Experience story-rich exploration as you dredge through untamed lands, face below zero temperatures, and uncover mysteries hidden in the snow. A journey into the long dark awaits!

name: Vending Dokan!: Kozy Kiosk
description: Build a vending machine empire in this cozy idle sim! Manage staff, decorate locations, and watch your business thrive. Play actively or let it run passively in the background with relaxing music to enjoy while you work or unwind.

name: Tides of Annihilation
description: Tides of Annihilation is a fantasy action-adventure inspired by Arthurian legend. Uncover the mystery of an otherworldly invasion in a shattered modern London, unleashing hordes of enemies. As Gwendolyn, fight alongside spectral knights to save your family and piece a broken world back together.

name: Armored Core: Master of Arena
description: Behind the scenes in Isaac City, two corporations are embroiled in a vicious fight for control and supremacy over the general populace. During one of the most violent encounters between the corporations, a large number of innocent civilians are caught up in the chaos and perish. One survivor, a young man, loses his entire family. A few months later, the embittered survivor decides to take action and exact revenge; his target is the pilot of an AC. That pilot is simply known as "Hustler One", and he pilots the AC around which events on that tragic day played out. In order to discover more and track down his quarry, the young man seeks out recruitment with the Ravens' Nest. And so, another Raven enters the fold…

name: Armored Core: Project Phantasma
description: A Raven operating out of Isaac City receives an unusual request. Not only is the request both vague and cryptic, stating simply: "Infiltrate the underground urban complex, Amber Crown,", but it also bypasses normal channels of communication and is sent directly to the Raven in question, without anyone else seeing the message. No sender name or corporate affiliation is mentioned, but the monetary reward promised is massive. Because of the amount, the mission will obviously be intensely dangerous, but Ravens aren't the type to shy away from any challenge. With interest piqued, the Raven climbs into the AC and heads toward Amber Crown.

name: Armored Core
description: Armored Core is a mecha video game released in 1997, now back for modern consoles.

name: Undertale: Papyrus' Belief
description: A take on the Disbelief project owned by FlamesAtGames where the roles of Sans and Papyrus are reversed in the no mercy route!

name: Flesh Made Fear
description: Tank controls. Fixed cameras. Pure Terror. Set in a haunting world of twisted experiments and occult nightmares, this game brings back the survival horror mechanics you know and love while pushing the genre into terrifying new depths.

name: Disaster Arms: Impact Project B.A.H.N.
description: Disaster Arms is a 2D run-and-gun boss rush game. Shoot and punch your way through a ceaseless gauntlet of giant alien and robotic lifeforms.

name: Five Nights at Freddy's: Blood & Gears
description:
"You hoped you'd never have to return to this place of sorrow, but after 20 years, something has called you back."

FNAF: Blood & Gears, created by JDBRYANTdev, is a ground up reimagining of the original Five Nights at Freddy's game by Scott Cawthon.

name: TurboSquad
description: TurboSquad is a racing party game where you don't drive but sabotage the race! Use traps, weapons and sneaky tactics to outsmart your rivals. Play solo, online or locally in colorful tracks full of loops, jumps and surprises.

name: Sleep Walk
description: This sleepy little penguin surely wouldn't like to be woken, given the bizarre and scary challenges he faces in order to get back home to bed. Can you help?!

name: Siegecaster
description: An active skill-based siege defense game. Prepare your aim and quickly assess the coming onslaught. Survive a large-scale assault on your home as you build outward to strengthen your arsenal. Engage epic hordes. Encircle powerful upgrade runes. Enhance your weapons. Siege the day.

name: Super Magic Chess
description: Super Magic Chess is an online mobile strategy game that combines chess strategies with card game mechanics, where you can create your deck with over 100 cards and make unique moves, and offers both a classic chess-inspired and innovative gaming experience.

name: Touhou Makuka Sai: Fantastic Danmaku Festival Part III
description: "Touhou Makuka Sai ~ Fantastic Danmaku Festival Part III" is a bullet hell shooting game with an arcade golden age style. It is the third game in the Touhou Makuka Sai series. The strange moon seems to hide a new conspiracy. Charge into the deep world on the eternal night!

name: Sil and the Fading World
description: Battle against fearsome Raidbosses alone! Uncover your past in Aritas, a sinister world ravaged by ancient Gods of the Realm Below. This ARPG features 9 class specializations, hundreds of unique items, a vast array of skills, complex character progression, and intense Raidboss encounters.

name: Calyx
description: A strategy game with a new kind of enemy, Calyx puts you in charge of a space mining outpost, locked in battle with an overwhelming alien organism. Build your base, gather resources, assemble your forces, and take on the Calyx. With only an out-of-date AI for company, can you survive?

name: Shadow Adventure
description: The game is Shadow's own Adventure, with the resurrection of Professor Gerald Robotnik, learning about a counter part to Chaos from Sonic Adventure 1, Destructo. Learning this, Shadow must take Gerald out.

name: Webstore Mogul
description: Rise to become a webstore mogul by managing your own online shop. Set prices for your products, manage inventory, hire employees, and design your online store. With strategic decisions and effective management, you will build a successful online business.

name: Tales of Ancients
description: Tales of Ancients is an atmospheric exploration game that tells the story of a man struggling to survive in a deserted town while tracing an ancient cult. In this world filled with heavy rain and mysterious rituals, you will uncover dark secrets.

name: 2004Scape
description: Lost City is a unofficial non-profit project focused on preservation through open-source emulation accessibility.

name: Stones Keeper II: Chaos Lord
description:
In Stones Keeper II: Chaos Lord, you'll immerse yourself in a fantasy world as a leader of a squad of the Circle of Unquenchable Thirst. Along with recruiting, leveling, arming, and providing for your army, you'll be in charge of your very own flying fortress. Growing it and improving its system will prove invaluable to challenges ahead.

You'll be able to create a unique squad, by recruiting new warriors with a multitude of skills and weapon preferences. The tasks that will be assigned to you will require not only the strength of your warriors, but also cunning. The search for valuable artifacts, raiding cities, subduing enemy commanders, desecrating lands, and capturing altars are only a few of the challenges you will face.

Every choice opens up opportunities. Change tactics and try new powers. In "Stones Keeper II: Chaos Lord" all means are good to leave your mark on history, be it force, diplomacy, or magic! Your decisions will determine the fate of the kingdom.

name: Biofactory
description: Build your living factory using organs and fleshy biomachines. Combine your pulsating machines to automate and scale up production. Mine, harvest, produce and assemble weird materials in a grimdark biopunk setting. No enemies or pressure, the hive mind has only one instinct: The factory must grow.

name: Dancing Pandas: Ranger's Path
description: Calling all animal lovers! Become the ranger for Summery Islands! Find courage by helping other Pandas. Dancing Pandas: a cozy adventure where bravery blooms beyond your comfort zone.

name: The Pub Life Simulator
description: Open your own pub with The Pub Life Simulator, serve food and drinks to keep your customers happy. Enjoy this exciting simulation experience solo or with friends. Unlock higher-quality products, expand your pub, and build the best business in town!

name: Mechanized Corps: Rebirth
description: Mechanized Corps: Rebirth drops you into the war-torn year of 2361, where Mechanized Corps fight for control of the Sol system's resources. Choose from four customizable classes, arm yourself with devastating weapons, and fight in intense squad-based combat. Battle offline or online with friends!

name: Dinkum Together
description: 'Dinkum Together' is a pioneer life simulation game currently being developed by 5minlab, a Krafton studio, and is inspired by 'Dinkum', the beloved survival life sim created by Australian developer James Bendon.

name: Musestruck
description:
A 2D Platformer RPG about art and magic. You play as JOURNEY and QUINN, two young artist friends who explore a mysterious magical world called NEGATIVE SPACE, to try and make it back home.

Journey must use his powers of illustration, and Quinn must use her powers of music to defeat comical and strange enemies, while slowly uncovering Negative Space's secrets, as it tests and strengthens the two's friendship along the way.

name: Tryhard
description: Turn-based sports RPG about managing an underdog rugby club in New Zealand. Outsmart opponents and upgrade your squad, but also feed your dog and go on dates, in this epic saga of love, betrayal, and community sports.

name: Laundromat Manager Simulator
description: Step into the world of Laundromat Manager Simulator—where your entrepreneurial skills and creative flair combine to transform a modest laundromat into a bustling business empire! Manage every detail, from upgrading state-of-the-art equipment to designing a standout interior, as you attract loyal customers and outshine the competition. Whether you’re a savvy strategist or a creative decorator, this is your chance to build the ultimate neighborhood laundry hub. Success is just a spin cycle away, are you ready to take it?

name: Pokémon/Grand Order
description: "Pokémon/Grand Order" is a fangame that adapts the story of Fate/Grand Order, using resources from the original game and adjusting them to Pokémon mechanics, based on the Fate system.

name: Leadlight
description:
Do you like pixel mosaics? Try a new approach at it with Leadlight!
Assemble stained glass mosaic from small shattered pieces - move, rotate and blend colors! Leadlight is a unique puzzle experience with 100 images for you to assemble.

name: Magic Chess: Go Go
description: Experience MLBB's multiplayer strategy game – MCGG! Unleash your magic and dominate the chessboard!

name: Iron Convoy
description: Iron Convoy is a turn-based tactical survival game set in a brutal post-apocalyptic world. Manage your convoy, battle enemies, gather resources, and make tough decisions to survive. In this unforgiving world, only the strongest endure!

name: Alquiem
description: Alquiem is a new Medieval RPG in which you will be able to gain strength through numerous classes and talent trees, professions and equipment to face the creatures that inhabit the lands of Odenzur. Its old-school style will remind all browser game fans of a familiar memory of Fighting, Loots and Relaxing.

name: Frozen Ship
description: Frozen Ship is a first-person narrative adventure in the unique blending of survival, build&craft, and economic strategy genres.

name: Moon Rat
description: A charming platformer game about a Rat who embarks on an adventure where you collect cheese with properties that are out of this world.

name: Noelle: Lost Soul
description: Noelle: Lost Soul is a DELTARUNE fangame set during an alternative ending of the Chapter 2's Weird Route.

name: Static Dread
description: Lovecraft meets Papers, Please. Play as a lighthouse keeper and guide ships safely into the harbor using your radio. Survive the presence of something impossible, and don’t let the shadows consume you!

name: Superhuman
description: superhuman is a visual novel full of battles and romance developed at Ren'py.

name: When Tails Gets Bored: Special Edition
Motocross Urban Fever
description: Motocross Urban Fever is a 3d sports game developed by Miniclip and Silent Bay Studios that was currently unavailable to play. It features 9 stages, 3 types of races, 3 race tracks, numerous airborne stunts, and 3 racers for players to pick: Miniclip Fury, Green Lizard, and Flaming Skull. It is the second of the three Motocross Fever series of games after Motocross Fever.

name: Smile, you're being filmed together
description: Dive into an intense psychological horror experience with Smile, You’re Being Filmed: Together, the multiplayer version where observation and cooperation are your greatest assets.

name: Nack the Weasel
description: The sniper gets a game all of his own, mixing many elements such as shooter, puzzler and platformer

name: 100 Ways to Kill the Crazy Frog
Sonic the Hedgehog: Hands of Time
Sonic the Hedgehog: The Freedom Fighters
Nightmare Kart: The Old Karts
description: An upcoming free expansion to Nightmare Kart with a brand new mini-campaign, racers, karts, tracks, power-ups, and game modes.

name: Kwun Tong
description: Made in Hong Kong. By Unreal Engine 5.4.4. Escape from Kwun Tong.

name: Armored Hongfeng
description: "Armored Hongfeng" is a TPS game with "tank vehicle" + "MOBA" gameplay. You will use famous active and retired tanks to compete on the battlefield. The game combines the strategic depth of traditional tank battles with the excitement of MOBA games, bringing an unprecedented gaming experience.

name: The Forgotten Deity
description: The Forgotten Deity is a refreshing action game with a 2D pixel art style, in which blocking is an important mechanism for the exciting offense and defense battles. You will take back your beloved dog from the hands of the Goddess of Light and get involved in the game of the gods.

name: Restart ShuHan Dynasty: Origin
description: Restart ShuHan Dynasty：Origin is an immersive interactive video game set in the history of The Three Kingdoms from the perspective of "Liu Bei", which incorporates modern anecdotes and suspense elements. Every choice you make will directly or indirectly affect the end of the game.

name: Satoyama Note Spring Walk
description: Satoyama note Spring walk is a point-and-click visual novel in which you aim to reach your destination while identifying plants in a satoyama in spring. Listen to the animals, observe and identify the plants as you make your way through the forest, and have lunch under the cherry blossom trees!

name: Kanon no Kakin Nikki
description: It is a multi-ending simulation game where you strive to become an alchemist. Along the way, discover new endings through encounters with different people.

name: Variable Puzzle
description: 《Variable Puzzle》is a strategy puzzle game.Challenge your intelligence and unleash your strategies! Come and try various challenges, enter the wonderful world of the game, explore the deep secrets of puzzles, and demonstrate your decision-making and thinking abilities.

name: Escape from the nightmare
description: This is an action-adventure game similar to an escape room. During the game, players need to find a key and a door to escape, while also avoiding the pursuit of nightmares.

name: Zhuishu
description: Can you hear it? The faint sound coming from an abandoned radio, calling out for forgotten children. Trace back a chilling tale lost to time and unravel the mysteries hidden within the ruins. Who is silently watching you? And who lurks within the fog, waiting for answers?

name: Mini Kingdom War
description: English is a medieval strategy war game where you can freely choose your faction, acquire resources, purchase armies from crystals, strengthen yourself, defeat enemy armies, break down enemy walls, and destroy enemy crystals to win the game. You can compete with AI and invite friends to play online.

name: Stray of Lost Cat
description: Welcome to "Stray of Lost Cat" ,where your mission is to save a cat with a peculiar personality. Learn how to deal with the suddenly appearing "Mischief," collect soul fragments scattered across different scenes, and embark on a relaxing and healing adventure~

name: Mushroom Tower Defense
description: Magic Mushroom Defense is a creative tower defense game where players defend their castle against magical mushrooms in 200 unique maze-like levels. Strategically place and upgrade towers, adapt to evolving enemies, and overcome challenging obstacles to protect your kingdom.

name: Sorcerer's Servant
description: It is a roguelike spinning RPG where you turn slots to strengthen equipment and fight monsters. By chaining equipment with slots, you can strengthen your abilities and upgrade to new equipment. Use your skills to lead her to victory.

name: Devil's Wish
description: This game is a fictional themed casual game that mainly tells the story of two young girls. Players will play as one of the blue haired girls named Cao Dan. After encountering Cao Dan, Liu Lian'er, who had thought she could escape poverty, was caught up in a shocking conspiracy.

name: Black Mystery: Wujing
description: Hot Blood NPC man hit bottom! Kill for love! Follow in the footsteps of the Big brother to the West! Sha Wujing is the protagonist this time! Seriously play, have a good rest, just do it!!!

name: Grindset T.V.
description: You have sinned, and Two-Day Delivery is the path to righteousness. Transport packages for the CEO of the Catholic Church, His Holiness the Cyberpope. Trick-based chaos meets corporate blasphemy in this unhinged speedrunning FPS. Your salvation isn’t free. But your suffering is priceless.

name: Sonic 4
description: A Sonic game which was being produced by VibrantDarkness and Cinossu, shown as a secret title at SAGE 9. Information about it is scarce, its SAGE booth didn't get properly archived. According to the page, Sonic, Tails and Knuckles would be in the game. No release date was given.

name: Unfamiliar Lands
description: A story-driven, exploration-centric, fantasy adventure game with timed action boss fights filled with magic, mystery and puzzles.

name: Project SXU
description: A project that aims to recreate the cancelled 1996 Sega Saturn title Sonic X-treme as close as possible, while adding original ideas and concepts from X-treme.

name: Blaze Rush
description:
Blaze Rush is a 2.5D platformer similar to Sonic Rush but it only features everyone's favorite lavender feline, Blaze The Cat!
Boost through levels and see if you can beat your record time while smashing and burning robots along the way!

name: Sonic Infinity Adventure Pack Season 2
description: Get ready for Funky Action Season 2! Get ready to reunite with the world's famous hedgehog on a high-speed cinematic adventure! And get ready to Explore stunning new worlds in speeds and in ways like never before! This upcoming rendition of the Adventure Pack is a remaster to an Infinity fangame classic that also expands upon the gameplay experience with new speeds, new levels, new areas, and new heights! This demo contains Abyssal Dungeon in it's entirely, one of many expansive levels in the Adventure Pack, all created with the Infinity Engine feel in mind.

name: Hamster Hunter: Rodent Rampage
description: A fast, crazy boomer shooter where mutant hamster-men kidnap you.. and regret it. Bust out of their creepy underground lab with big guns, smash through their evil plans, and turn every furry freak into bloody chunks on your way to freedom.

name: NeoFables
description: First fully AI generated VR (WebXR) storytelling experience. Create your own storyline, character, and world, with total freedom to explore and interact.

name: Deltarune Wandering Makers: Pantheon of the Discarded
description: Taking off from the original storyline, you explore a strange new "darker-than-dark" world, looking for "shadow bosses" to battle for their "Shadow Crystals"

name: Oxide: Survival Island
description:
Here you are, alone on the abandoned island, where everything can kill you. Cold, starving, predators, enemies: are you strong enough to tackle all these dangers?
Now stop, breathe and plan. Step 1: gather resources and create tools. Step 2: build a shelter and make some attire. Step 3: craft weapons, chase animals and procure food. Don’t forget about other players inhabiting this island. Make allies to fight alongside! Ready? Steady, Go! Do your best to stay alive! Good luck!

name: Prop Haunt
description: Prop Haunt is a multiplayer horror game where you play as either an investigator reporting haunts or spirit that is trying to grow their influence and scare other players. Choose either preventing spirits from taking hold or embrace the horror and try to increase your influence to be the strongest spirit.

name: Lost Lost Lost
description: An adventure puzzle game where you explore a colorless city to find hidden red, green, and blue color balls, solving challenges to restore vibrancy to Relax City.

name: The Legend of the Heroes of the Water Margin
Animal Connect Fusion
description: Animal Connect Fusion is a delightful and engaging game with simple yet captivating gameplay. Players collect animals by connecting those located close together, forming the brightest straight line. The more animals connected, the higher the score.

name: Trump Breakout
description: This is a retro-inspired game that pursues the fun of block crumbling. The design is reminiscent of the PCs of the 80s, creating a nostalgic atmosphere.

name: VA Action collection
description: Three action-packed shooters with gripping stories, intense combat, and unforgettable challenges.

name: Desktop Cat Cafe
description: Build your dream cat cafe in this tiny cozy management sim that lives at the bottom of your screen! Unlock exciting new recipes, decorate your space with our wide variety of goodies, and hire cute staff to take care of the cafe while you're doing other things.

name: Fellowship
description: FELLOWSHIP is a multiplayer online dungeon adventure set in an exciting fantasy setting, with endlessly scaling dungeon runs.

name: Reactoryx
description: Immerse yourself in the captivating world of intrigue and investigation in “Reactoryx,” a unique detective game featuring hidden object searches, challenging puzzles, and uncovering mysteries that could change the course of history.

name: Crossovertale
description:
Play as Frisk all grown up after the ending of Undertale.

FIGHT or SPARE your way through a brand new world, where characters from all across the video game multiverse come together and wage battle

name: Unizone's Underswap: Distrust Sans
description: A take on the events of the Swap version of the famous "Disbelief Papyrus" Alternative Timeline

name: Angel's Lullaby
description:
Angel's Lullaby takes place during the game's opening introduction, back during the Human and Monster War. Expanding on the lore, meta narrative and core themes of the original games, Angel's aims to enrich the Undertale world by mixing both the old and new.

Combining both an open-world and linear story-line, Angel's is an ambitious fangame with a large story to tell. There's three main "Acts," each with it's own main area that follows a story.

name: Black Raven
description: Black Raven is a dark 2.5D action-adventure rooted in Slavic Folklore set in 14th-century Eastern-Europe. Play as Ivan, a man consumed by vengeance after a brutal raid shatters his family. Journey through grim landscapes and fight brutal enemies in this dark tale of loss, rage, and resilience.

name: Shawarma King
description:
Celebrating 20 Years of "Falafel King" with a Modern, Flavorful Twist!

Welcome to Shawarma King, where you’ll discover what it truly takes to become the undisputed ruler of the street food empire!

Transform your small shawarma stand into a culinary empire while navigating the challenges of rising taxes, demanding customers, and unpredictable suppliers. Inspired by the classic Israeli game, "Falafel King," this modern homage comes with a new twist, tons of humor, and plenty of challenges.

Will you succeed in turning your small shawarma stand into a culinary empire spanning cities? Or will you end up under investigation by the tax authorities?

name: Cardtographer
description:
Cardtographer is a stylized 3D-Graphics Roguelike Deckbuilder, in which you choose one or more Champions to fight the evil, which has overcome the lands.

During your adventure your chosen champions gain gold and experience during the fights and enhance their deck to overcome their opposing enemy finally.

You also can ally with your frineds in online coop.

name: Superstition BlackCat
description: A roguelite where superstitions take shape as items! Face enemies, collect drops with negative effects that can be traded for advantages. Explore always different rooms, with challenges inspired by beliefs that make us think twice before taking a risk.

name: Panzer Dragoon Voyage Record
description:
Panzer Dragoon Voyage Record is an upcoming virtual reality title currently being developed by Wildman inc. it is a compilation that will allow players to experience various episodes from the original Panzer Dragoon Sega Saturn games.

Panzer Dragoon Voyage Record was unveiled on March 10, 2020, the 25th anniversary of the original Panzer Dragoon. The game was originally scheduled to be released in the 2020 Japanese Fiscal Year (which went until March 2021). However, its crowdfunding was delayed until 2021, so the current release window is unknown.

The game will be published by Wildman Inc., with Sega having no investments in the project; Watanabe has accepted the risks, arguing that if Sega was financially involved and the game failed, it would damage the Panzer Dragoon franchise, which he wants to avoid.

name: Battle Run
description:
Ready, set, RUN! Welcome to Battle Run! The adrenaline-pumping party racing game loved by millions of fans is back!

From the studio behind Tap Titans 2 and the popular Beat The Boss franchise, comes the return of long-awaited and fan-favourite real-time running multiplayer game - Battle Run!

Escape wicked rockets, evade spinning axes, and navigate past sneaky hazards - it's the ultimate race to the finish line!

Party up and play with your friends in an action-packed race and charge into first place! Become a racing legend as you outrun your opponents and compete in real-time multiplayer battles!

With runner’s like Ryder and his volcanic rain, Dust’s high-speed skateboard, and Macie’s explosive leap, it’s an attack blitz waiting to happen!

Revamped with all-new Runners, explosive items, and racing across vibrant worlds, this is Battle Run like never before.

name: Sonic Battle 4: The Call to Chaos
Git Gud
description: Git Gud is a fast-paced, 3D precision platformer designed for 1-4 players. If you love speedrunning, bunny hopping, and intense platforming challenges, this is your game.

name: Robin Hood: Sherwood Defenders
description: As the legendary Robin Hood, fight the Sheriff's forces in the open field by defending the Merry Men's allies from invasions in this tower defense game. Produce resources, build up your fortifications, place units, and then join in the battle yourself!

name: Deltarune: Internal Demons
description:
One day, the trio found themselves caught between getting caught from the teachers around the corner, or risking everything and jumping into the strange grey door. Leaving their school and world behind.

After a long fall Scuta wakes alone, with only one option to go, he has to proceed further, finding his friends and leaving the new dark world.

name: Undertale: Thanatos!
description:
MT EBOTT. 202X
Legends say that those who climb the mountain never return.
You, as the new fallen human, possess the power to manipulate the world.
But your actions have shown such power can easily corrupt your mind.
Your own curiosity, resulted in a mass extinction. Repeating the same events over and over again.
But nothing is meant to last forever.
Your very own power has consumed you. And now consequences of your actions are finally crawling up your back.

Are you ready?

name: Kangaroo Court
description: Kangaroo Court is a chaotic, satirical courtroom simulator for 4-40 players. Play as Judge, Defendant, Prosecutor, or Defense Lawyer, with roles like Jury, News Crew, Police, and more. Defend or incriminate the defendant, vote, and decide their fate based on their crimes!

name: NCORE
description:
This is a free PvPvE multi-arena shooter in the format of an entertainment show.

Fight alongside your teammates in a virtual multi-arena for the right to become NCORE champions! Your task is to eliminate opponents and collect as many coins as possible or prevent other teams from doing so. You can move between hexes, raid bosses, ambush other players, or charge straight into battle. Plan your strategy carefully and do whatever it takes to win in NCORE!

name: Metal Sonic Quest 2: Return and Revenge
Dimension Escape
description: Dimension Escape is a tactical card game. Choose your heroes wisely—will you pick a ninja pirate or a robo dinosaur? Equip them with powerful ability cards and defeat all who stand in your way.

name: Dotu
description: A game that combines math with the challenge of logic-based puzzles. Place dots on the board to match the target sums of rows and columns. Each world brings new twists to test your brainpower.

name: Mechaknights Legends
description: As the pilot of a massive mechanical armor, you will face powerful dragons and dangerous creatures dwelling in the darkest corners of the world.

name: Inconceivable Rat Endeavour
description: Embark on a wacky rat's endeavour in this genre-bending hexagonal puzzler. Rotate hexes to make your way out of miserable sewers, collect inconceivable amounts of cheese, avoid deadly traps and prepare for silly surprises.

name: Swarm Racer 3000
description: Swarm racer seems to be as much a puzzle game as it is a racing game.

name: How to Date an Entity (and stay alive)
description: This game is a Visual Novel game with a length of about 15 to 20 minutes (per ending—so it actually takes some time to get all of them). It’s about an MC who wakes up in their room and encounters a tall mysterious woman. He must date her to survive. The game incorporates elements of both Dating Sim and analog horror, featuring a total of 10 possible endings. All endings based on "Interest Meter", so you need to be aware of it.

name: Rayman Lum'o'Grams
description:
Rayman Lum'o'Grams is a puzzle fan game for PCs running Microsoft Windows currently in development by Rayman Universe, or RUNI.

The game belongs to the Picross/Nonograms genre and uses both its own and assets of most 2D projects from Rayman series, with the exception of UbiArt games. The game was first announced at Rayman Alive 2022 as part of the RUNI Showcase segment presenting Rayman Universe projects, which featured a concept trailer. The project's World Premiere took place at Rayman Alive 2023, revealing most of the details of the game. The first public demo version has been announced for early 2024, but its released has been postponed.

name: Unmourned
description: Unmourned is a first person psychological horror game where you play as Jason, a man who moves into a new house only to be haunted by escalating paranormal activities. As the disturbances grow more intense, Jason discovers that the house's previous owners mysteriously vanished. Driven by terror and desperation, Jason must uncover the truth behind the family’s disappearance and find a way to break the curse that now haunts him. Can he solve the mystery before it's too late?

name: Candleholder
description:
You play as Spamton, who has fallen in a Neo Dark Fountain inside Kris's pocket, and now explores a strange, dreamy place called the Cluttersphere.

With your perspective shifted, having Jevil as your ally (?) and being tasked with protecting Kris's lifeforce in the form of a candlelight, you must use the SOUL to guide Spamton into making it back to the Dark World safely.

name: Undertinge
description: Play as the Wizard named Frisk. Welding magic as a weapon, you have to end the Eternal Night, destroying the heart of darkness that plagues the land, freeing the world from the wicked clutches of the ancient curse. Will you let the darkness blind you? Will you make it out alive? Well, that, my friend, is up to you to decide.

name: The Evil D
description: Square up against THE EVIL d, the letter with the most VILE attitude you have ever seen! He’ll throw everything he has left at you in hopes of maintaining his title of the most dastardly letter alive. Will you succumb to his wrath and let him control the fate of the world as he pleases, or will you fight for all that is good? Regardless of the outcome, you best prepare yourself for the ruthlessness of THE EVIL d!

name: UnderTale: DoctorTale
description:
DoctorTale is a crossover fan-game based on the sci-fi series Doctor Who (by BBC) and the RPG game UnderTale (by Toby Fox).

The plot tells of the Time Lord from Gallifrey, traveling across different planets that are imprisoned in one large Pocket Universe which is on the verge of self-destruction. In this world, you can go the way of mercy to save everyone, or you can use brute force to achieve personal freedom. You decide, the fate of the universe is in your hands.

name: Necrosis: Dawn of Dread
description: Necrosis: Dawn of Dread is a FPS co-op survival horror game.

name: The Directorate: Novitiate
description: Become Mercury, a powerful, magical gangster in this thrilling third-person Action RPG. Fight supernatural threats, track a serial killer across Los Angeles, and choose sides as war breaks loose.

name: Demiurgos
description: Demiurgos is a competitive strategy god game where you wield divine powers to convert followers, outmaneuver rival deities, and reshape the world. Choose Good or Evil, Chaos or Order, and forge your path to dominance. Inspire devotion or instill fear—the choice is yours.

name: Stains of Regret
description: Stains of Regret is a short 2D horror experience following the story of a father looking for his daughter. Follow his journey learning more about the world and its characters as you attempt to find your daughter, all whilst having to face unspeakable horrors and personal demons.

name: Guilty as Sock!
description: Enter a chaotic courtroom where socks play lawyers, prosecutors, and judges! Use absurd evidence, craft wild arguments, and deliver verdicts in this hilarious online party game. Improvise, strategize, and shout "Objection!"—because in Guilty as Sock!, chaos always wins!

name: Roulette Dungeon
description: Roulette Dungeon is a turn-based rogue-like where you spin a roulette wheel to defeat your enemies. Master the balance between strategic planning and unpredictable luck by placing bets, using special abilities, and collecting items to outsmart your foes and conquer the dungeon.

name: Isadora's Edge
description: Can you keep going when all hope is lost? Isadora's Edge is a 2D Action Platformer with a unique future fantasy setting. Explore an alien world, battle against the corrupted forces bringing it to the edge of destruction, and uncover the secrets behind its impending demise!

name: Withering Realms
description: A ghost and her doll guardian explore the mysterious town of Penwyll and the sprawling graveyards, tombs, caves and rotting estates that surround it in this Horror Action RPG from the creator of Withering Rooms.

name: Hoover Heroes
description: Hoover Heroes is a physics-based multiplayer party game for up to 8 players to play online, featuring cute and silly cleaners. Funny animations, colorful graphics, and fun mechanics will keep you laughing every moment.

name: Supercar Collection Simulator
description: Supercar Collection Simulator is a game where you sell surprise car boxes to earn money, build a car collection and engage in exciting races with rivals.

name: Jumpers League
description: A competitive online multiplayer platformer where every jump is a gamble. Climb to the top while using strategic abilities to outsmart your opponents, but beware: one misstep can cost you all your progress.

name: Deltarune: Broken Destiny
description:
Deltarune: Broken Destiny is a tale set in the original Deltarune universe.
We see a new part of Deltarune's world away from Hometown.

name: Is This Seat Taken?
description: Is This Seat Taken? is a logic puzzle game where you play matchmaker for groups of hilariously particular people. Each character has pet peeves that make seating them a delightful challenge. Find the perfect spot for each person to unlock new levels in this cozy, silly, and relatable experience.

name: Before Arthur
description:
Lead your people through the dark ages in this blend of medieval grand strategy and RPG simulation. Rule your kingdom while navigating the life of a monarch; battling the elements, religious strife, disease, and political treachery. Will you survive as a Briton, or conquer as a Saxon?

Set in the dark ages during the Saxon invasion of Britain, you choose your faction and design your first character who will forge your dynasty. As you go about living your character's daily life you will be building and managing your small kingdom, deciding where to place buildings, what laws to pass and who's other kingdoms to invade.

The Bench
description: Relax on a park bench, find hidden objects, solve quirky puzzles, and fend off pesky pigeons in this charming, interactive adventure. Enjoy beautifully stylized, colorful levels keeping you entertained!

name: Tower of Babel Survivor of Chaos
description: Battle hordes of monsters, acquire new skills, and upgrade your abilities. Customize your build with hundreds of item combinations and reach the top to fulfill your deepest desires. Conquer the tower in this thrilling roguelite hack and slash survivors game!

name: Puzzle Spy International
description: Pursue a ring of diamond thieves and their trail of cryptic puzzles in this ‘60s spy adventure. As Agent Epsilon you’ll choose your path as you chat with (or chat up!) suspicious contacts. Decode cryptograms, decipher clues and deduce answers as you solve wordplay & logic puzzles across the globe!

name: Projekt Godhand
description: An extremely high-speed "keyboard destruction rhythm game" in which any key on the same half of the keyboard can be used to input notes.

name: Sniper at Work
description: Sharpen your aim and embrace chaos in this action-packed single-player sniping experience. Scout targets, plan creative kills, and adapt when things go sideways. With dynamic missions, tactical freedom, and explosive surprises, every shot tells a story. Precision or mayhem - the choice is yours!

name: Town to City
description: Build an idyllic 19th century Mediterranean town and help it flourish into a prosperous city. Freely place and customise each element to create the perfect home for your growing population in this cozy city builder from the creators of Station to Station.

name: Project Shikai
description: A multiplayer first-person arena fighter delivering competitive, fast-paced anime-inspired combat with the strategic depth of traditional fighting games.

name: J.League Excite Stage '94: Nagoya Grampus Eight
J.League Excite Stage '94: Panasonic Gamba Osaka
J.League Excite Stage '94: Nissan F.C. Yokohama Marinos
J.League Excite Stage '94: Sanfreece Hiroshima FC
Am I Nima
description: Am I Nima is a psychological-horror game where you must convince your mom that you really are her daughter. Combine words together in your brain and use them to talk. Get her to trust you.

name: Star Iliad
description:
Star Iliad is a Metroidvania adventure game set within this celestial leviathan - now in development!

Dive into the guts with Star Iliad, a retro-future action adventure game. Play as Blythe Braves, a star ranger stranded within the labyrinthine organs of the mythical Star Whale. Fight fearsome foes, sling spells and bullets, and befriend a charming set of castaways in your quest to escape.

name: NightFell
description:
Trapped in a forgotten world atop an enchanted mountain, Monsters have been confined to an endless darkness. Life on the CROWN is dangerous and hopeless, with many monsters turning to cruelty to stay sane.

On Halloween night, Jackie accidentally stumbles into this terrifying realm. They're told the only way out is at the highest peak of the mountain. With that in mind, Jackie sets out to climb to the top with their best Friend, Flowey.

Will they forge friendships with the battle-worn residents that call this Hell a home? Or will they succumb to the ruthless law of this land... "Kill or Be Killed?"

name: Underswap: The Reckoning
description: Out of all the possible paths you can possibly entwine yourself into, this one in particular will prove to really challenge your palette.

name: Deltaruined
description: Deltaruined is a mod of DELTARUNE, the Toby Fox's lastest game to the date. This mod includes both chapter 1 and 2. Enjoy Completely new battles! New Cutscenes! (original cutscenes reworked too!), new mechanics and a lot of unused content restored!

name: Dusttale Reimagined
description:
Ever wanted an Undertale fangame that completely re-builds (or rather, REIMAGINES) the concept of Dusttale from the ground up?
Well you're in luck! This game is just for you!
Explore the Underground, meet old friends in new situations and join us in this race for DETERMINATION against Flowey your best friend in Dusttale Reimagined!

name: Desktoptale
description: Desktoptale is a tiny program that puts a fully controllable Undertale, Undertale Yellow or Deltarune character of your choice on your Windows desktop!

name: Underswap: Echoed
description: “Underswap: Echoed” is the Breakfast Bunch’s reimagining of the popular Undertale AU, Underswap.

name: Undertale Plus
description: Undertale Plus is a mod that allows you to have your own completely customized Undertale experience! Bringing all-console exclusive content of the original, with widescreen support, colored sprites, custom battle backgrounds, bug fixes, and many more with add-ons.

name: Team Delusional's Dusttale
description: Team Delusional's Dusttale is our own take on the well-known AU: Dusttale, which in itself is a fangame of Toby Fox's Undertale. You will face many new roadblocks as the entirety of the underground questions your motives, and a familiar hooded figure looms over your every move. Will you choose the easy way out this time, or will you strive for a better tomorrow?

name: Plane Destroyer
description: Plane Destroyer is an Infinite-Runner indie game where the galaxy is in trouble and you are the one to save it!

name: F-Zero: Falcon Densetsu e+ - Traditional Park (Dragonbird)
F-Zero: Falcon Densetsu e+ - Expansion Park (Golden Fox)
F-Zero: Falcon Densetsu e+ - Explosion Track (White Cat)
F-Zero: Falcon Densetsu e+ - Ballute (Astro Robin)
F-Zero: Falcon Densetsu e+ - Junction (Blue Falcon)
Undertale: Call of the Void - Placek's Take
description: Undertale: Call of the Void [Placek's Take] is an alternate interpretation of Undertale: Call of the Void, originally created by Saster and J-Bug. Developed by Placek and the COTW Team, this version introduces multiple unique endings, enhanced graphics, and fresh twists while preserving the signature Call of the Void style.

name: Deltarune: Hypothesis
description: A Deltarune fangame featuring a collection of hypothetical scenarios, each imagined as a fully playable segment of gameplay. Discover the hidden mysteries that connect these scenarios as you dive into each one, unraveling an existential truth about you and every adventure you’ve been on so far.

name: Deltamon
description: Explore the vast region that Kris calls home as you aid them in becoming champion! Your rivals Susie, Noelle and Berdly join alongside you to see and catch over 200+ pokémon from Kanto to Paldea!

name: Deltafall
description:
Deltafall is a Deltarune AU where the original trio discovers that their school was built after a science facility that conducts dangerous experiments with the dark world.

In 1977. A top secret corporation has found a way to harness the power of dark worlds to create any worlds they wanted. IDEATION INC has one goal. To create the perfect world. For all lifeforms. Not bound by reality. But bound by imagination.

name: Vision Crew's Deltarune: Alternate Chapters
description:
Vision Crew's Deltarune: Alternate Chapters is a fangame project aiming to interpret Toby Fox's earlier concepts and Chapters, it's entirely speculative and plans to be worked on even once his own content is out!

It includes familiar characters, even ones Toby has namedropped without a design... or vice versa! But you'll also meet a ton of brand new characters!

name: Dual Cat: Max
description: Join Max, the brave and clever cat, on a puzzle-platformer adventure to save his best friend, Erwin

name: Petal Crash 2
description: The freshest in arcade puzzle action blossoms again! Crash blocks together into dazzling chain reactions in a puzzle like no other - now completely refreshed with refined gameplay, arcade graphics, brand new game modes, and dazzling special attacks!

name: Max Manos
description: Max Manos is an incremental destruction game where you play as a powerful hand, known as Max Manos, eliminating shapes. Chain explosive reactions, collect shards, and upgrade your abilities to destroy shapes even faster.

name: Steel Judgment
description: Steel Judgment is an ultra-fast roguelike movement FPS full of wacky combos and weapons that combines the expressive combat of beat-em' ups with the unhinged chaos of a roguelike. Wipe out hordes of enemies with a diverse moveset and arsenal while collecting powerful items with unique effects.

name: Elevator Music
description: You make the elevator go up, go down, go fast, and go slow. And yet, by the end of the week in an old hotel below looming Edelfaustian mountains, you'll have been the deciding factor in either war, or peace.

name: Gravity Storm: First Mission
description: Break the laws of physics, dash and shoot your way through levels full of hazards and machines gone rogue. In this retro game, you control Project Gravity Storm an advance machine able to control gravity itself; however, the mother computer will not make things easy for you.

name: Street Li Fang Zhuan
description: Street Li Fang Zhuan is a Chinese micro horror game set in 1980s China, combining the story of understanding puzzles and text adventures. In the game, the scroll scene that can be moved by four axes is applied to bring different game experience to the player.
